t: Fotronic Corp - Company Profile and News - Bloomberg Markets
s: Fotronic Corporation, doing business as Test Equipment Depot, provides test equipment solutions. The Company offers new and refurbished equipment, brand promotions, and application notes.

t: About Us - At Test Equipment Depot
s: Incorporated in 1992 and based in Woburn, Massachusetts, Test Equipment Depot is a veteran-owned distributor of high-quality test equipment and tools. We have developed long-standing relationships with premier test and measurement equipment manufacturers.

t: Shop all of our great Brands at the Test Equipment Depot
